title: 1.0 - DICOM Rewrite / Redesign
description:
For a while, I have been adding significant features and functionality to this library but maintained much of the core design of the upstream forks (go-dicom). 

As I've written in many issues and prior refactors, I think that a more maintainable and extensible design is warranted, so I've started a ground-up rewrite/refactor of the library, currently at s/explore branch (soon to land on a separate 1.0 branch).
